snippet.title: Nonolith Gameplay 1
snippet.description:
An early gameplay teaser for my upcoming game; Nonolith. 
In this puzzle platformer, you learn the secret rules as you go. 
You're insanely powerful, you just don't know it yet. 
This world holds more than you know. 

Coming to Steam later in the year, for now you can follow the project at:
https://x.com/justcamh
https://mastodon.gamedev.place/@justcamh
https://bsky.app/profile/justcamh.bsky.social
